item.title: Ministry of Commerce
item.description: ß· This article is about a ministry of the Vekllei Interior Parliament Overview # COSMOSOL The Vekllei Ministry of Commerce (COSMOSOL) regulates and initiates trade in the country. Despite the functional moneylessness of the Commonwealth, COSMOSOL remains among the busiest ministries of the Interior Government, since all economic policy, international trade and entitled renumeration (the Vekllei turn-of-phrase for withdrawing from the Labour Bank) occurs through its subordinate commissions.
